# iShot Concept — environment variables
#
# Booking form email delivery is handled by Web3Forms (https://web3forms.com),
# a free service that emails form submissions with no backend of your own.
#
# SETUP
#   1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter the address that should RECEIVE
#      booking inquiries (e.g. ishotconcept01@gmail.com). You'll get an Access Key.
#   2. Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is git-ignored) and paste the key below.
#   3. Restart `npm run dev` (or rebuild) so Vite picks up the value.
#
# NOTE: This is a public *submit* key by design — it only lets the site POST a
# form to your inbox and is safe to ship in client-side code. It is NOT a secret
# that grants account access.

VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
